text: Adolphe Jules Grisel was a athlete and gymnast from France. Adolphe competed at the 1896 Summer Olympics. He was born on 9 December 1872 and died on 13 December 1942.Adolphe Grisel ==References== == Other websites == * Category:1872 births Category:1942 deaths Category:Olympians for France Category:French athletes Category:French gymnasts Category:Sportspeople from Paris
